title: Mega collection - Knit dolls, toys and Christmas ornaments
description:
Mega Collection - Knitted dolls, doll clothes, toys, Christmas ornaments 

A large collection of books, booklets and standalone patterns divided into three categories folders: Dolls, Toys, Christmas ornaments. Dolls also includes dolls' clothes. 
They are NOT my own uploads, but gathered here and there over the years. What I did is open or preview them to see what they are and consistently rename them so that the titles reflect the actual title of the book or booklet - this enabled me to immediately remove duplicates. 
If is was part of a series (Sirdar, Daisy-May etc), the issue number is provided. 
In very many cases, I've included in brackets what size doll the clothes are for, so that you can easily pick the ones you need. For fashioin dolls, I've put "Fashion doll" on top of the title, so that they are all grouped together. 
Some of them are cleaned up (because of bad scanning), but very few, as it's not a category that interests me a lot. 
However, I see there is a demand for it, thus I'm uploading it. 

The files are loose, so that you can pick the ones you want. 

Please note: I share my bandwidth with an all-day gamer, so I am only able to seed at night and early morning. And I live in Europe so my night might be your day. Thus be patient if I am away when you try to download. Just leave it on, and you will be OK.
